{
  "stem": "19198.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 144.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, later on, I became very much aware of the political reality of anti-Semitism because Eberbach was an early stronghold of the Nazi party, starting in the-- certainly by the mid '20s, probably even by the early '20s.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The-- the major industry in town was a factory that was owned and certainly controlled by two of Hitler's closest friends and supporters, and Hitler frequently visited town in order to be in consult with those people.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And both the president and the manager of the-- of the company became major-- played major roles in the-- Hitler's government.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The president of the company was a man by the name of Kepler, K-E-P-L-E-R, who I believe played a role in the Foreign Service under Hitler.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the manager's name was Pleischinger, P-L-E-I-S-C-H-I-N-G-E-R, and I don't remember what post he had under Hitler.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were a chemical factory and they manufactured an ingredient for the making of-- of motion picture and photographic film.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And their major customers directly or indirectly were the American film industry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember my father meeting with Mr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Lemley, who was one of the major powers in-- in the film industry, when he visited relatives in Frankfurt and tried to convince him that they should not buy anything from-- from this firm because they were a major support for the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was called Odin [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Verka, ?] O-D-I-N, named after the great Germanic god, Odin.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I-- I would think by the mid or certainly late '20s, this was a well established fact that these were active participants in the Nazi movement, that if you wanted a job there, you had to join the party and if you were physically and age-wise the right person, you had to join the SA.",
      "word_count": 56
    }
  ],
